Usage: parse_proc_arguments [-help] <result_array> [<forced_proc>] -args <string>
-help              # Prints out the command usage
<result_array>     # array to hold results (string, required)
<forced_proc>      # name of the invoking procedure (string, optional)
-args <string>     # Specifies the list of arguments passed to the Tcl procedure (string, required)